      The purpose of this table is to create a link between Skill properties (from the raw data) and modifiers/multipliers used for calculating stats in ChroniCalc 
      Example: For skill Redemption, the value stored in the "DAMAGE" property on the Skill object will be used to modify the HOLY_DAMAGE multiplier in ChroniCalc
  -->

